From 0c0c863964154d3e706176e3f8d4f4b132330c2b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: JesseJohn7 <JesseJohn7@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Jul 2026 09:55:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(template_versioning): add optional deprecation reason

- Add deprecation_reason: Option<String> to TemplateVersionRecord,
  stored alongside the deprecated flag and readable via get_version
  (the existing version-query read path).
- deprecate_version now takes an optional reason param; existing
  callers can pass None to preserve prior behavior.
- Include the reason on the TemplateVersionDeprecated event so
  off-chain indexers get it without an extra query.
- Add tests covering deprecation with and without a reason, and
  update existing call sites for the new signature.

Closes #789
---
 .../contracts/template_versioning/src/lib.rs  |  16 +++
 .../tests/test_versioning.rs                  | 129 +++++++++++++++++-
 2 files changed, 139 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

